{"tid":2422571,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[Netflix 新番] 天空侵犯","createTime":"2021-02-25T09:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T04:33:26.000Z","uid":12110,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"2f2f4a1f4fdcd9518b2c9a70c7733cec6fe2cf93","tid":2422571,"uid":12110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/78/52eae0250e4e765654c7ec57a81acku5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F78%2F52eae0250e4e765654c7ec57a81acku5.JPG&h=535ff4fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/79/bd64585e36df9cbebbb3939b8e1ackv5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F79%2Fbd64585e36df9cbebbb3939b8e1ackv5.JPG&h=9b2dc719&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《天空侵犯》故事描述，本城遊理突然來到一個莫名其妙的世界，這裡放眼望去只有超高大樓與吊橋，還有個戴著面具的殺人魔在她面前殺人。遊理為了逃離殺人魔的追殺，所以拼命逃跑，但大樓的樓梯卻沒有通往地面，只能在高樓層與屋頂移動。遊理試著撥打手機，沒想到哥哥接了電話，而且哥哥竟然也在這個奇怪的世界裡。為了逃離這個只有超高大樓、吊橋與殺人魔的世界，遊理決心活下去並展開一段殘酷的生存遊戲。<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n原作：三浦追儺<br />\n漫画：大羽隆廣（講談社 週刊少年マガジン編集部・DeNA「マンガボックス」連載）<br />\n監督：たかたまさひろ<br />\nシリーズ構成：待田堂子<br />\nキャラクターデザイン・総作画監督：植田羊一<br />\n総作画監督：牛島勇二、五十内裕輔<br />\n美術監督：谷口純基（アートチーム・コンボイ）<br />\n美術設定：根本洋行（アートチーム・コンボイ）<br />\nプロップデザイン：小川浩<br />\n色彩設計：小針裕子<br />\n撮影監督：田中浩介<br />\n3DCGディレクター：菅友彦<br />\n編集：宇都宮正記<br />\n音楽：tatsuo、酒井陽一<br />\n音響監督：たかたまさひろ<br />\n音響制作：セイバーリンクス<br />\nアニメーション制作：ゼロジー<br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n本城遊理：白石晴香<br />\n二瀬真由子：青木志貴<br />\n新崎九遠：関根明良<br />\n本城理火：榎木淳弥<br />\nスナイパー仮面：梅原裕一郎<br />\n相川守：福山潤<br />\n日下部弥生：日笠陽子<br />\n沖原真司：緒方恵美<br />\n青原和真：遊佐浩二<br />\nアイン：安済知佳<br />\nディーラー仮面：伊藤静<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Cqhr0Nv2FBU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCqhr0Nv2FBU&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=844dd063\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Cqhr0Nv2FBU</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BgOObVZp2Gs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBgOObVZp2Gs&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=d57e9c4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BgOObVZp2Gs</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><p class=\"center\"><span class=\"red\">Netflix:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.netflix.com/title/81043571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Ftitle%2F81043571&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=87a1ec5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.netflix.com/title/81043571</a></span></p></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6c011e5e02718fb3d89f719ad3f20af98ff6f0d8","tid":2422571,"uid":12110,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:27:15.000Z","msg":"岩岩見出左<br />\n漫畫睇評論好似係垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知有冇伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f24ed6c2f4254b8f085792370b50fca30dc1da","tid":2422571,"uid":206522,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:27:48.000Z","msg":"開頭唔錯, 可惜漫畫爛尾"},{"pid":"578d4b87b831ed27c6359323a01f1e78e66b0218","tid":2422571,"uid":240467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:28:35.000Z","msg":"爛尾作"},{"pid":"88889d25b572bd67e6165085f641c8659dce63a3","tid":2422571,"uid":141869,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"6c011e5e02718fb3d89f719ad3f20af98ff6f0d8","tid":2422571,"uid":12110,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:27:15.000Z","msg":"岩岩見出左<br />\n漫畫睇評論好似係垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知有冇伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"垃圾到仆街,<br />\n最撚垃圾係佢居然可以出第二部<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589dc5118eca11d8a3e379bd4bcd17